aradhana ( english : worship ) is a 1969 indian romantic drama film directed by shakti samanta , starring sharmila tagore and rajesh khanna . it was voted as the best film of the year by the filmfare awards . sharmila tagore would win her first filmfare best actress award for playing the lead role in this film . originally released in hindi and dubbed in bengali , aradhana 's huge success led to two remakes , both starring vanisri in tagore 's role : the tamil film &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; selvan ( 1974 ) and the telugu film &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ( 1974 ) . this film is counted among the 17 consecutive hit films of rajesh khanna between 1969 and 1971 , by adding the two hero films marayada and andaz to the 15 consecutive solo hits he gave from 1969 to 1971 .